{
  "stem": "10.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I show you records I have seen here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we took it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this way, they were able to make the trials.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we collected it for about one-- then [INAUDIBLE] from Nordhausen, we were transported to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was in Western Germany-- the whole unit there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there we remained only maybe two weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we went back to Wiesbaden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is near Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this was the headquarter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there we stayed up to the trial of Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I got my papers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And yeah, then during the time I was working, two days after [? the ?] liberation, my captain said, Sieg, take the Jeep, go up to the displaced person camp.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The concentration camp was immediately changed to a displaced person camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because what do you do with the tens of thousand people?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where do they go?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no communication, no railroad, no post, no telephone, nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what did you do?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They opened displaced persons camps, and they flooded them with food from America, from England, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people, so many people, died from overeating.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They got sick.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They couldn't take it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I begged them, please, eat slowly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You are like a baby.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "First, the mother milk, and then you get the cereal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You didn't eat for four, five years this kind of food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You will get sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Eat slowly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You don't have to worry about tomorrow because there's much left here yet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You will have it [? forever. ?] No, the [? eyes ?] ate [? everything. ?] And my friend in Poland, this way too-- he over-- he was so fat.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I kept-- I didn't eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I ate normally every meal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then two days after, he sent me upstairs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm coming upstairs to DP camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I find a friend from Poland, a nurse from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, Sieg, how are you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm glad you're alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What are you doing?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, I work for some Americans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, why don't you stay overnight here?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have a little party.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Can you imagine?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Two days after liberation, the prisoners, they partied already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Food was there, everything, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I said, OK, I will stay.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I [? stopped ?] a soldier there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the GI go down and tomorrow, pick me up in the morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we're sitting in a room, and benches around.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And here next to me, two young girls, Polish girls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we start to talk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From where are you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What are you doing?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What you have in mind to do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after a while, I ask, tell me, are you Jewish?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She jumps at me-- how dare you to ask me this kind of a question?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, you know, quiet down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are liberated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You have nothing to worry anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You should be proud that you are Jewish and you survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So she admitted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this is my wife.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was with another girl, the younger girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I took them in the evening to the barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I stayed with other friends of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Next morning, the soldier picked me up and I went down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm coming down, I see they're preparing a transport to France.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "French prisoners, concentration camps, they were sent back to France.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said to the captain, you know, I have two young girls upstairs in the DP camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They don't know where to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They cannot go to Poland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They don't know if they have relatives, who is alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Can they go with them to France?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
